{"tid":2137170,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁凱晴報名參選立法會","createTime":"2020-08-02T16:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T17:02:00.000Z","uid":117412,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8c71ca35bc4003db34cb50e0ea65ef430bc881","tid":2137170,"uid":117412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"【我報名參加咗一個已經取消的立法會選舉】<br />\n <br />\n時常有人問我，政府下一步是甚麼？習近平會怎樣對付我們？我不是預言家，亦不想做政權傳心師，不能剖析瘋婦、小學生的行為。大家唯一知道的，就是暴政不可能給予我們喘息的機會。<br />\n<br />\n先係DQ12人，再以疫情DQ 今年選舉，未來還會藉大型武肺檢測收集港人DNA。說實話自上年六月以後，已經知道此極權的荒誕。但有如此一着，雖然心裡早有個底，但時辰來到，心情也是複雜的。<br />\n<br />\n政權不惜加速攬炒香港，向反抗者報復，我們一方面被壓得難以喘氣，另一方面政權亦進一步搾取香港的僅餘價值，同時引來更強國際輿論壓力。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個被DQ的選舉底下嘅參選人，參選嘅初衷就係想為抗爭留一點血脈，繼續奮鬥。因為大家可以看得到，香港現在只剩下了一條向前的單行線。長路漫漫，要繼續前進，就只能嘗試一切方法，無論空間有多窄。縱使前路有幾多阻滯，大家都只能繼續向前，因為已經再冇退路。<br />\n<br />\n出年有冇選舉？會DQ咩人？我哋無從稽考，但大家有嘅係彼此，有嘅係信念，有嘅係不滅嘅決心。呢個時候可能大家仲係未消化得哂，過去兩日，自己同團隊都依然思考緊未來抗爭的出路。但最起碼，我們還有一些陣地需要固守，作為月華區區議員，定當繼續在亂世，在疫情中與社區同行。我相信大家香港人依然會繼續同行！<br />\n<br />\n#社區為家 #晴繫月華<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n📸【Instagram】<br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/leunghoichinglhc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fleunghoichinglhc&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=0593c4ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/leunghoichinglhc</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/kwuntongfuture\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fkwuntongfuture&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=d08c3ec1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/kwuntongfuture</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n不屈火苗 存亡號召 Ballot, or Bullet"},{"pid":"973a9f22e80fb1f346797452213f562e8b75b592","tid":2137170,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc662cfc65ea109a2313b5d04346665cfd50320","tid":2137170,"uid":117412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/za6zjUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fza6zjUA.jpg&h=422d15bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba7619cf2d897db41f7c5f16c32146913a644349","tid":2137170,"uid":117412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"973a9f22e80fb1f346797452213f562e8b75b592","tid":2137170,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"Hi國安"},{"pid":"9b461d775d244a35fb9d93027f179a228b3a7a43","tid":2137170,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"細腦粒議員"},{"pid":"6551fca0dd632f8e79538f26e3bc405f6a2fb60b","tid":2137170,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b461d775d244a35fb9d93027f179a228b3a7a43","tid":2137170,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"細腦粒議員"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"細細粒議員"},{"pid":"8400cebfa515cff3ac2f647f59fb0054bc9cac2f","tid":2137170,"uid":117412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6551fca0dd632f8e79538f26e3bc405f6a2fb60b","tid":2137170,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b461d775d244a35fb9d93027f179a228b3a7a43","tid":2137170,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"細腦粒議員"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"細細粒議員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"9萬一個月想比佢包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab73aeb194f040562e116549ac3bdf30a514b74","tid":2137170,"uid":71632,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"咁大波一定